# cast ai annotate --dry-run (SIMULATION — see demo/sim/cast-sim.sh).
Output demo/gifs/ai-annotate.gif
Set Width 940
Set Height 470
Source demo/tapes/_setup.tape

Hide
Type `source "$CASTREPO/demo/sim/cast-sim.sh"` Enter
Type "clear" Enter
Show
Sleep 400ms

Type "cast ai annotate --dry-run" Sleep 600ms Enter
Sleep 4s
